description: Sharpen your tongue while you sharpen your sword with this Monkey Island-style insult sword fighter! You'll face a series of five insults with multiple choice responses. Can you hold your own in this battle of wits? Ask insult sword fighter to start a new game to begin a duel!
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask insult sword fighter to start a new game.
name: Insult Sword Fighter
shortDescription: Relive the glory days of pirating with this insult sword fighter!
